00:00:41.666 --> 00:00:42.686 A:middle
content they love.

00:00:45.336 --> 00:00:47.336 A:middle
My name is Tommy Payne.

00:00:47.966 --> 00:00:48.866 A:middle
My friends call me T.

00:00:48.866 --> 00:00:50.996 A:middle
Payne, and I'm a designer here

00:00:50.996 --> 00:00:51.436 A:middle
at Apple.

00:00:53.066 --> 00:00:55.196 A:middle
Growing up in Australia, the

00:00:55.196 --> 00:00:57.496 A:middle
rest of the world felt very far

00:00:57.496 --> 00:00:59.496 A:middle
away, and I was searching for

00:00:59.496 --> 00:01:00.446 A:middle
ways to connect.

00:00:59.496 --> 00:01:00.446 A:middle
ways to connect.

