I was interested and curious

00:01:02.426 --> 00:01:03.686 A:middle
about other cultures, other

00:01:03.686 --> 00:01:05.346 A:middle
people, different areas and

00:01:05.346 --> 00:01:06.136 A:middle
environments.

00:01:07.176 --> 00:01:12.456 A:middle
So I looked to TV and movies to

00:01:12.696 --> 00:01:14.006 A:middle
bridge that connection.

00:01:15.116 --> 00:01:16.406 A:middle
And I would come home from

00:01:16.406 --> 00:01:18.736 A:middle
school, plunk down on the couch,

00:01:18.896 --> 00:01:19.906 A:middle
and turn on the tele.

00:01:20.786 --> 00:01:22.056 A:middle
And I would start to channel

00:01:22.146 --> 00:01:25.936 A:middle
surf, flicking up and down until

00:01:25.936 --> 00:01:27.496 A:middle
