00:01:27.896 --> 00:01:29.306 A:middle
And when it did, I was

00:01:29.366 --> 00:01:30.186 A:middle
captivated.

00:01:30.186 --> 00:01:31.866 A:middle
I was engrossed.

00:01:31.866 --> 00:01:34.066 A:middle
I was drawn into that story.

