00:38:07.076 --> 00:38:08.686 A:middle
property on your view controller

00:38:08.686 --> 00:38:09.796 A:middle
embedded within your Tab Bar

00:38:09.796 --> 00:38:10.266 A:middle
controller.

00:38:10.986 --> 00:38:11.926 A:middle
We generally recommend this

00:38:11.926 --> 00:38:13.136 A:middle
style for collection views full

00:38:13.136 --> 00:38:14.066 A:middle
of browsable content.

00:38:14.306 --> 00:38:15.566 A:middle
In fact, UI Collection View

00:38:15.566 --> 00:38:16.596 A:middle
Controller does this for you

00:38:16.596 --> 00:38:17.266 A:middle
automatically.

00:38:17.766 --> 00:38:19.526 A:middle
If you'd like the Tab Bar to

00:38:19.526 --> 00:38:20.546 A:middle
stay fixed at the top of the

00:38:20.546 --> 00:38:21.746 A:middle
screen, you can just leave this

00:38:21.746 --> 00:38:22.636 A:middle
property nil.

00:38:23.716 --> 00:38:25.586 A:middle
In either of these cases, you

00:38:25.586 --> 00:38:26.646 A:middle
should be mindful of the safe

00:38:26.646 --> 00:38:26.936 A:middle
area.

00:38:27.256 --> 00:38:28.596 A:middle
For scroll views, you'll get the

00:38:28.596 --> 00:38:30.186 A:middle
right behavior for free if you

00:38:30.186 --> 00:38:30.596 A:middle
just set the

00:38:30.596 --> 00:38:32.026 A:middle
contentInsetAdjustmentBehavior

00:38:32.026 --> 00:38:33.116 A:middle
to automatic.

00:38:33.316 --> 00:38:34.446 A:middle
If you're doing your own layout,

00:38:34.446 --> 00:38:35.106 A:middle
you can use your view

00:38:35.106 --> 00:38:38.186 A:middle
safeAreaLayoutGuide to help you.

00:38:38.296 --> 00:38:40.096 A:middle
We're also adding some new API

00:38:40.096 --> 00:38:41.756 A:middle
UITabBar so you can reflect your

00:38:41.756 --> 00:38:42.726 A:middle
branding in your apps.

00:38:43.286 --> 00:38:44.846 A:middle
We've added a new area to either

00:38:44.846 --> 00:38:46.536 A:middle
side of the Tab Bar where you

