00:44:58.166 --> 00:44:59.576 A:middle
this, the Masked Amount

00:44:59.576 --> 00:45:01.316 A:middle
specified by the layout in cell

00:44:59.576 --> 00:45:01.316 A:middle
specified by the layout in cell

00:45:01.316 --> 00:45:02.016 A:middle
would be zero.

00:45:03.146 --> 00:45:04.546 A:middle
But when we're browsing around

00:45:04.546 --> 00:45:05.996 A:middle
in inset from the sides like

00:45:05.996 --> 00:45:07.806 A:middle
this, the Masked Amount is one.

00:45:08.416 --> 00:45:11.316 A:middle
