00:45:40.396 --> 00:45:41.706 A:middle
relative to the Masked Content

00:45:42.246 --> 00:45:42.366 A:middle
View.

00:45:43.376 --> 00:45:45.426 A:middle
The same information is passed

00:45:45.426 --> 00:45:46.506 A:middle
