understand some of the

00:46:19.656 --> 00:46:20.806 A:middle
parameters that you can use to

00:46:21.066 --> 00:46:22.266 A:middle
get exactly the effect you're

00:46:22.266 --> 00:46:22.706 A:middle
looking for.

00:46:23.256 --> 00:46:26.056 A:middle
Since there are a lot of pixels

00:46:26.056 --> 00:46:27.136 A:middle
moving around in a full screen

00:46:27.136 --> 00:46:28.656 A:middle
layout like this, we have some

00:46:28.656 --> 00:46:30.126 A:middle
best practices that we recommend

00:46:30.126 --> 00:46:31.106 A:middle
for getting the most out of

00:46:31.106 --> 00:46:31.766 A:middle
TVCollectionView

00:46:31.766 --> 00:46:32.436 A:middle
FullScreenLayout.

